Below is a complete A-Frame Web VR application that loads a simple world featuring a chat window with five characters (Gary, Darnell, Zongleborg347, Chotox, and larryb3) discussing how to fry an egg. Additionally, the world includes 10 randomly sized buildings, each with 6 to 10 stories and a total of 64 windows (16 on each side).

